::{{DIcon|Talk}} Is it okay to spill your secrets like this?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414250023-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' Don't worry. A lot of members in the Alchemy Commission know about the forbidden tomes, and some of them have a reputation for having loose lips.
:::'''Yuluo:''' Retrieving these tomes won't be easy if we rely solely on our own intelligence network. That's why I need your help with this. After all, it is Madam Qingzu from the Seat of Divine Foresight who recommended you to me.
:::'''Yuluo:''' Since I need your help, it's my duty to tell you everything I know about this issue, otherwise it'd be a hassle, right?
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I can't guarantee that I'll find them...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414250027-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' Don't worry. I understand how tough this task is, and I'm not expecting you to bring them back anytime soon. We have no clue what Lady Dan Shu or the Disciples of Sanctus Medicus did, after all.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_414250030-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414250030-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' So, you need to retrieve these three scrolls: The ''Manuscript of Wisdom'', the ''Manuscript of Silence'', and the ''Manuscript of Delirium''. While I don't have many leads on them, I'll do my best to answer any questions you might have.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_404025001_48-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_404025001_48-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} The ''Manuscript of Wisdom''?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414250032-->
::::'''Yuluo:''' Once, an illiterate person read this book and suddenly became incredibly intelligent. Although they weren't on par with the members of the Genius Society, they became way smarter than ordinary people.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} The ''Manuscript of Silence''?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414250034-->
::::'''Yuluo:''' Once, a blind person read this book and claimed that they could hear the Sound of Silence, although no one knows exactly where such Sound of Silence comes from.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} The ''Manuscript of Delirium''?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414250036-->
::::'''Yuluo:''' Once, a reckless person tried to read this book, but as soon as they opened it, they started convulsing and then passed out.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I see. I'll come back to you once I find them all.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414250038-->
