::{{DIcon|Talk}} I heard that the remnants of the Disciples of Sanctus Medicus are causing trouble here.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502049113-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' Oh, I heard about that on my way back. I'm surprised you know about it too.
:::'''Yuluo:''' It seems to be true. The Cloud Knights have sealed off some areas and are hunting them down.
:::'''Yuluo:''' Still, I have no idea about the details...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} How did you become the chief alchemist?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502049117-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' I have no clue. I was participating in a medical conference outside the Luofu when I was suddenly notified of the promotion via a message.
:::'''Yuluo:''' I left the conference halfway and quickly packed my bags. When I got back, not a single soul was there to arrange the handover.
:::'''Yuluo:''' I was told that something huge had happened, and the Cloud Knights were doing an investigation, so everything had to be put off. So, I'm left here, clueless.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Do you have the lowdown on the situation?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502049121-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' Huh? Lowdown? What happened again? How come I didn't hear anything?
:::'''Yuluo:''' What on earth happened? *Sob* Why has no one told me about it? If you find anything, please share it with me as well.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} How come you don't know anything?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502049124-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' How should I know!? I really don't know anything!
:::'''Yuluo:''' I wasn't even away for that long! Why do I feel like the whole world has changed? Is this still the Alchemy Commission I know? What happened...?
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} Forget it. I don't have any more questions.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502049127-->
:::'''Yuluo:''' About Lady Dan Shu... Life truly is unpredictable...
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502049102-->
;(If {{Mission|Obsequies Performed, A Long Road Ahead|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:{{DIcon|Talk}} How's your life as the chief alchemist?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502049301: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502049301.json-->
::'''Yuluo:''' I'm more familiar with the job now, but I still don't think I can handle it. I'm just not cut out to be a leader.
::'''Yuluo:''' Ugh, I just can't take it. I spend every day thinking about how to escape to another planet...
::'''Yuluo:''' But I can't do it. As you know, the public image of the Alchemy Commission has been greatly undermined after what took place previously. I know most healers and alchemists aren't cultists, and they need my support.
::'''Yuluo:''' Although the future is challenging, the Alchemy Commission will regain the people's trust.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502049301-->
