::'''Yuluo:''' Looks like the ''Manuscript of Wisdom'' is quite dangerous indeed. Thankfully, it hasn't caused any severe consequences so far.
::'''Yuluo:''' Perhaps this ''Manuscript of Wisdom'' is not meant for humans, but rather to break the bans of ingenia... As you know, all ingenium creations have been deprived of their wisdom after the Aurum Rebellion.
::'''Yuluo:''' If this is the case... we were really lucky that it didn't cause any disasters while it was in the wrong hands.
::'''Yuluo:''' Thanks to your help, all the lost forbidden tomes have been safely returned without causing any calamities.
::'''Yuluo:''' Madam Qingzu was right to have faith in you. Without your help, it would have taken me forever to find these lost manuscripts...
::'''Yuluo:''' Here's your hard-earned payment. I might need your help again in the future. See you then.

