::'''Yuluo:''' Of course, this is detrimental to their mental health, and will have an impact on their social life... That's why the ''Manuscript of Silence'' is listed as one of the forbidden tomes.
::'''Yuluo:''' So, don't worry. Lady Dan Shu has been gone for a long time, and Xiaoyu is just an innocent girl who misses her too much.
